values.label: TF_NODIAGONAL
values.comment: 'HoverOver' in SA clients and later, to determine if tiles can be moved on by flying gargoyles

values.label: TF_NOSHADOW
values.comment: Disallow shadow on this tile, lightsource? lava?

values.label: TF_PIXELBLEED
values.comment: Let pixels bleed in to other tiles? Is this Disabling Texture Clamp?

values.label: TF_MULTIMOVABLE
values.comment: Movable multi? Cool ships and vehicles etc?

values.label: CF_BIT_LBR
values.comment: 0x08 - Enables LBR features: mp3s instead of midi, show new LBR monsters

values.label: CF_BIT_AOS
values.comment: 0x10 - Enable AoS monsters/map, AoS skills, Necro/Pala/Fight book stuff - works for 4.0+

values.label: CF_BIT_ML
values.comment: 0x80 - Elven race, new spells, skills + housing tiles

values.label: CF_BIT_TENTHAGE
values.comment: 0x400 - Splash screen for 10th age - crystal/shadow house tiles

values.label: CF_BIT_SA
values.comment: 0x10000 - Enable SA features: gargoyle race, spells, skills, housing tiles - clients 6.0.14.2+

values.label: CF_BIT_HS
values.comment: 0x20000 - Enable HS features: boats, new movementtype? ++

values.label: SF_BIT_LIMITCHAR
values.comment: 0x10 - Limit amount of chars, combine with OneChar

values.label: SF_BIT_AOS
values.comment: 0x20 - Enable Tooltips, fight system book - but not monsters/map/skills/necro/pala classes

values.label: SF_BIT_SE
values.comment: 0x80 - Samurai and Ninja classes, bushido, ninjitsu (4.0.5a)

values.label: SF_BIT_SEND3DTYPE
values.comment: 0x400 - Send UO3D client type? KR and SA clients will send 0xE1)

values.label: SF_BIT_UNKNOWN4
values.comment: 0x800 - added sometime between UO:KR and UO:SA

values.label: SF_BIT_SEVENCHARS
values.comment: 0x1000 - Use 7 character slots instead of 5?6?, only 2D client?

values.label: SF_BIT_UNKNOWN5
values.comment: 0x2000 - added with UO:SA launch, imbuing, mysticism, throwing? (7.0.0.0)
